---

<PageLayout title="Laporan PPID - PPID SMKN 14 Jakarta">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8">Laporan PPID</h1>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full">
            <thead class="bg-primary text-white">
              <tr>
                <th class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-sm font-medium text-primary">No.</th>
                <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left text-sm font-medium text-primary">Jenis Laporan</th>
                <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left text-sm font-medium text-primary">Nama Laporan</th>
                <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left text-sm font-medium text-primary">Periode</th>
                <th class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-sm font-medium text-primary">Download</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="bg-white divide-y divide-gray-200">
              {laporanPPID.map((item) => (
                <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50">
                  <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-sm text-gray-900">{item.no}</td>
                  <td class="px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-900">{item.jenis}</td>
                  <td class="px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-900">{item.nama}</td>
                  <td class="px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-900">{item.periode}</td>
                  <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center">
                    <button class="bg-primary hover:bg-primary-hover text-white px-3 py-1 rounded text-sm transition-colors duration-200">
                      ðŸ“¥ Download
                    </button>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              ))}
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Laporan PPID disusun secara berkala untuk memastikan transparansi dan akuntabilitas pengelolaan informasi publik.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</PageLayout>